課程概述 Course Description
 

課程學習目標 Course Objectives    
	    藉由對微觀下流體各種現象與理論的介紹使學生可以掌握流體特性並將所學應用到生醫工程領域。    

課程進度 Course Outline


週次 Week進度說明 Progress Description
1Introduction and History2Fluid Mechanics Theory I3Fluid Mechanics Theory II4Fluid Mechanics Theory III5Digital Microfluidics6Droplet Manipulation7Micro Fabrication : Soft Lithography8PDMS-based Microfluidic Chips (Lab work)9Mid-term Report10Experimental Flow Characterization (Lecturing & Demo)11Microfluidics for External & Internal Flow Controls12Sensor Principle and Microflow Sensors13Mass Transport and Cellular Microfluidics14Microparticle-Based Assays15Microfluidics for Lifescience and Chemistry16Fluidic Self-Assembly (FSA)17Emerging BioMicrofluidics and Clinical Applications18Final Report 

　以上每週進度教師可依上課情況做適度調整。The schedule may be subject to change.


